<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Halas Hates Gnolls Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Visit Blackburrow and kill gnolls to retrieve some gnoll fangs.<BR>
<BR>
2) Head to Halas and visit the Warriors' Guild.  Talk to Lysbith McNaff to receive the quest.<BR>
<BR>
3) Give the gnoll fangs to Lysbith one at a time and she will give you some small change, some exp., and a ration.<BR>
<BR>
**Be careful, this quest lowers your faction with the banker in Halas.**</div>
<BR>
