<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Like just about every quest in the game, you can do this multiple times. If you went to Halas with 15 stacks of gnoll fangs, she would just keep taking them and rewarding you.<BR>
<BR>
If you were wondering about the experience gain, it should give you a visible amount until 11th level or so.</font></td></tr></table>
