<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The only way that I've seen to raise Halas faction outside of Halas is to do the Kolianda fish aquisition quest in West Karana.  Once you give the "puke potion" to frostbite, you'll get steel warriors, wolves of the north the barbarian shamans faction up.  Unfortunately, to do this quest, you have to be able to get into surefall and into the zoo in Akanon.  You're best bet is to get either an enchanter to boost your faction for ya or to get wolf form cast on you for surefall...  Either way, it's a faction hell, but this might be a bit easier than trying to get by a bunch of angry barbarians = P.  <BR>
